src:
Jadwal Pertandingan Shopee Liga 1 Hari Ini, Senin 4 November 2019
04 Nov 2019, 09:16 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Kompetisi Shopee Liga 1 2019 telah memasuki pekan ke-27. Satu pertandingan pembuka akan digelar hari ini, Senin (4/11/2019).
Persela Lamongan akan menjamu Barito Putera di Stadion Surajaya, Lamongan.
Persela saat ini menempati peringkat 16 dengan perolehan 24 poin dari 25 pertandingan (M5 S9 K11). Sementara itu, Barito berada di posisi 12 dengan 29 poin dari 26 laga (M7 S8 K11).
Persela ingin keluar dari zona degradasi, jadi tiga poin pun mereka incar. Namun, Barito tentu tak ingin pulang dari Lamongan dengan tangan hampa.
Berikut jadwal lengkapnya.
text:
Shopee League 1 Match Schedule Today, Monday 4 November 2019
Nov 04 2019, 09:16 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Shopee Liga 1 2019 has entered its 27th week. One opening match will be held today, Monday (11/04/2019).
Persela Lamongan will host Barito Putera at Surajaya Stadium, Lamongan.
Persela is currently ranked 16th with 24 points from 25 matches (M5 S9 K11). Meanwhile, Barito is in 12th position with 29 points from 26 matches (M7 S8 K11).
Persela want to get out of the relegation zone, so they are aiming for three points. However, Barito certainly did not want to go home from Lamongan empty-handed.
The following is the complete schedule.
